    <li>
      <a class="txt-dn" href="mailto:?subject=Down+or+out%3A+The+future+of+fossil+fuels+at+COP28&amp;body=https://www.lowyinstitute.org/the-interpreter/down-or-out-future-fossil-fuels-cop28">
